# SafeHer — Auth + Profile Edit + Background SOS

## Summary of Problems

| # | Problem | Root Cause |
|---|---------|------------|
| 1 | User is auto-logged in on every launch | `restoreSession()` in `authStore.ts` reads from `AsyncStorage` and sets `isLoggedIn: true` with no user prompt |
| 2 | No login / signup option visible | Since auto-login fires first, the user never sees `auth/login` or `auth/register` |
| 3 | Cannot change name / profile | `settings.tsx` shows name but has no edit button; the `authStore.updateProfile()` API exists but is unused in UI |
| 4 | Background shake + voice SOS not working | Voice detection is **disabled by default** (`voiceKeyword: false`); users don't know how to enable it; no status indicator anywhere |

